Drive, unaware that a tornado was about to touch down. When the
wind suddenly picked up, the family looked out a window and saw
their dachshund's doghouse spinning four feet in the air.
</P>
<P>
   ``The dog was spinning around inside the doghouse,'' Diamond
said. ``It was like a Toto moment. My wife started hollering at me,
like it was my fault we had a tornado.''
