   MARKET-TECHNOLOGY (Undated) _ Blue Chip technology stocks
sustain heavy losses as mutual funds sold off their high-flying
technology stocks, bringing the week's decline in the Nasdaq stock
index to 10 percent. By Kimberly Blanton.
</P>
<P>
   BIOTECH-CONCLUDE (Boston) _ Biotechnology conference winds down,
with several protests. By Karen Hsu. 400 words.
</P>
<P>
   PEBBLE BEACH-LAWSUIT (Undated) _ Marshall's, Pebble Beach Golf
Course suing each other over rights to Pebble Beach line of
clothing. By Ralh Ranelli. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   CRANBERRY-LIMITS (Undated) _ Looking to lower its surplus and
boost prices, the cranberry industry asked the USDA to impose
limits on the amount of cranberries growers can bring to market. By
Chris Reidy. 500 words.
