<P>
   LIBBY-ASBESTOS (Seattle) _ Vermiculite from a closed mine in
Libby, Mont., where hundreds of workers and their families died of
asbestos-related diseases is still being sold in garden stores in
the Seattle area. The product, Zonolite Chemical Packaging
Vermiculite, was found to have alarmingly high levels of asbestos _
higher than the levels in other garden products _ in recent testing
by the Environmental Protection Agency.
